snippet.description:
Double Barrel Gaming Channel Bio:

Hello & welcome to Double Barrel Gaming. My name is Mr. BoomStick XL, and I've been the producer of this channel for about 5 years, with plans for many more! This channel Is dedicated to celebrating and discussing gaming in The Best Way Possible. We will NEVER use clickbait or console war nonsense to drive views, or subs. I'm honored to produce (5) weekly shows, the topics are well-researched for accuracy & explained in full detail during every LIVE show. Each week I invite a panel that represents the best of the gaming community and introduce you to new voices on the scene. Double Barrel Gaming is a place for gamers to get the latest news and information in a positive community environment. Thank you for taking the time to check out the channel. I hope to see you soon!

Hi, my name is Mike and my biggest passion is gaming. I want to share my passion with highly edited gameplay, Guides, Montages and everything else that is needed for a decent YT channel. My current focus is Hunt Showdown and everything that has to do with Survival Games and FPS. I also do lots of VR and from time to time I review games. See the "featured channels" section. (state: December 2021)

I hope you accompany me along the road to become a bigger Youtuber :) 

Stay connected via social media on twitter and facebook. Any questions? Drop them in the comment section!

snippet.title: 4FS Gaming
snippet.description:
Welcome to 4FS Gaming! We are an Australian based gaming group, dedicated to bringing you a range of gaming content. We have made a pledge to respond to the wishes of our fans. So, if you want to see us create a video on anything in particular, just ask!

We currently focus on content Hunt Showdown, but delve into many other games as well.

Use code "4FS" at the Crytek Store for discounts on Hunt: Showdown, DLC, and Crysis Remastered! https://shop.crytek.com/?ref=3485

Patreon Page: https://www.patreon.com/4FSGaming

snippet.title: Mythili Gaming
snippet.description:
Hello and welcome to my streaming channel! My name is Mythili and I am a girl gamer who is passionate about sharing my love of BGMI with the world.

I've been playing BGMI  Mobile for years now and have always loved the rush of landing on the island, scouring for weapons, and taking out my enemies. But what I love even more is the sense of community that comes with being a PUBG Mobile player. Whether I'm teaming up with friends or joining a squad with strangers, there's nothing quite like the camaraderie that comes from working together to take down the competition.

But BGMI Mobile isn't the only thing you'll find on this channel. I'm also a huge fan of all things gaming, from the latest releases to classic favorites. So you can expect to see a variety of content on this channel, including reviews, gameplay footage, and even some personal vlogs.

Thank you for joining me and I can't wait to see you in the chat!

For any business queries write to:
mythiligamingyt@gmail.com
